      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition. The exterior has significant rust, deep scratches, and multiple dents. The interior shows heavy wear, including tears in the upholstery and stained carpeting. Several mechanical components require repair or replacement to ensure reliable operation.",
      "price": 5500.0,
